## 2026-05-30 22:50 WIB — Section 14-27 batch close → **Router roadmap CLOSED**

Wrap-up batch — 14 sections closed dengan schema + minimal endpoint phase 1. Mesh stack (14-23) single-owner reality = schema only, real mesh logic defer phase 2 saat multi-host aktif. LLM/pricing/policy (24-27) full CRUD endpoint siap.

### Section 14-23 — Mesh stack (10 sections)

- **feat(internal/store/mesh_stack_migrations.go)** (NEW LOCKED): Migration ID 101 `section14_23_mesh_stack` — 10 mesh tables bundled:
  - **14 mesh_packets**: packet_id UNIQUE + origin_pubkey + packet_type + payload_json + signature + ttl=5 + hop_count + processed flag + 2 idx.
  - **15 mesh_gossip_state**: packet_id PK + seen_at + forwarded_to (dedup tracking).
  - **16 mesh_crdt_state**: PK topic+node_pubkey + counter + payload_json (vector clock per-topic).
  - **17 mesh_knowledge_inbox**: packet_id UNIQUE + drawer_content + status (shadow default) + idx status.
  - **18 mesh_tool_manifests**: PK tool_name+origin_pubkey + manifest_json + signature.
  - **19 mesh_peer_karma**: PK pubkey_hex + karma=0.5 default + promoted/dropped counters.
  - **20 mesh_filter_audit**: packet_id + filter_name + decision + reason + idx packet.
  - **21 mesh_lora_deltas**: model_name + origin + delta_uri + size + signature.
  - **22 mesh_l3_state**: WITHOUT ROWID kv (degraded mode).
  - **23 mesh_daemon_status**: WITHOUT ROWID kv (heartbeat).
- **feat(handlers_mesh_stack.go)** (NEW LOCKED): GET `/api/mesh/stack/overview` — row count per 12 mesh table buat diagnostic. Single-owner phase 1 expected mostly empty.

### Section 24-27 — LLM provider + LocalAI + pricing + policy

- **feat(internal/store/llm_pricing_policy_migrations.go)** (NEW LOCKED): Migration ID 102 — 6 tables:
  - **24 provider_chain_configs**: chain_name UNIQUE + providers_json (ordered array of provider IDs).
  - **24 provider_call_log**: caller + provider + model + tokens + cost_usd + latency_ms + status + 2 idx (time+caller).
  - **25 localai_models**: model_name UNIQUE + gguf_path + size_bytes + checksum + manifest + signature + loaded flag.
  - **26 pricing_rules**: UNIQUE (provider, model, tier='default') + input/output per_1m_usd + enabled + notes.
  - **27 policy_budgets**: UNIQUE (scope, scope_key, metric_key) + budget_value + reset_period (daily/weekly/monthly) + warning_pct=0.8 default.
  - **27 policy_violations**: budget_id + actual_value + action_taken + idx budget.
- **feat(handlers_llm_policy.go)** (NEW LOCKED): 6 endpoint CRUD:
  - GET/POST `/api/provider/chains` — UNIQUE chain_name upsert.
  - GET `/api/provider/calls?from=&to=&limit=` — call log query.
  - GET/POST `/api/localai/models` — model registry upsert.
  - GET/POST `/api/pricing/rules` — UNIQUE (provider, model, tier) upsert.
  - GET/POST `/api/policy/budgets` — UNIQUE (scope, scope_key, metric_key) upsert.
  - GET `/api/policy/violations?limit=`.

### Wiring (routes.go)

- 7 routes baru: mesh/stack/overview + provider/chains + provider/calls + localai/models + pricing/rules + policy/budgets + policy/violations.

