## 2026-05-30 11:55 WIB — Section 12: Discipline constitution (phase 1 propose+vote) DONE + LOCK

- **feat(constitution)**: `internal/constitution/proposals.go` (LOCKED) — propose+vote workflow library. Leverage EXISTING `constitution` table dengan `pending_quorum_review` column + auto-trigger `trg_constitution_log_update` (history archive). API: `Propose` (INSERT pending=1, UNIQUE source_file+section anti-dup, content 16KB cap), `ListPending` (cap 500, summary/include_content toggle), `Vote{approve|reject}` idempotent (re-vote returns no-op kalau already settled), `CountPending`. Single-owner phase 1: VoterID free-form via header `X-Voter-ID`.
- **feat(handlers)**: `handlers_brain_proposals.go` (LOCKED) — `POST /api/brain/constitution/propose` body ProposeOpts. `GET /api/brain/constitution/proposals?include_content=1&limit=` summary or full. `POST /api/brain/constitution/vote?id=&approve=0|1` header X-Voter-ID.
- **verified end-to-end via 10 scenario**:
  - Propose FQP-13 (anti-halu audit rule) → id=664 pending
  - Propose FQP-14 (lock-after-verify rule) → id=665 pending
  - Duplicate propose (same source_file+section) → UNIQUE reject
  - List pending summary (no content)
  - List pending include_content (full)
  - Approve 664 → status=approved (pending=0)
  - Reject 665 → status=rejected (deleted_at + deleted_by='vote-rejected:mr.dev')
  - Re-vote 664 → no-op (idempotent)
  - Vote on missing id → 'proposal not found'
  - Invalid approve param → 400
  - DB state verified: 664 promoted clean (pending=0, no delete); 665 rejected (pending=1 + deleted_at + deleted_by)

### Phase 1 scope (DONE):
- Propose + List pending + Vote workflow on existing schema.

### Defer phase 2/3:
- **Brain reset endpoint** (`POST /api/brain/reset?confirm=YES_NUKE_ALL`) — DESTRUCTIVE, defer sampai ada audit log + backup workflow
- **Multi-signer quorum auth** (current single-owner — VoterID free-form via header)
