## 2026-05-29 21:45 WIB — Section 7: Mistakes journal global (phase 1) DONE + audit + LOCK

- **feat(brain)**: tabel `mistakes_journal` di brain DB (id, category, title, content, source_agent_id, hit_count, tier='global', reviewed_at, promoted_to_antibody_id, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) + UNIQUE(category, title) + 4 index. Schema di `internal/brain/init.go::SchemaSQL`.
- **feat(brain)**: `internal/brain/mistakes.go` (LOCKED) — `SubmitMistake` atomic UPSERT via ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE dengan RETURNING (kills TOCTOU race), `ListMistakes(tier, source, limit)`, `CountMistakes(tier)`. Private `mistakeCategoryWhitelist` + `IsValidMistakeCategory()` + `ListMistakeCategories()` accessor (anti shared-state mutation). Validation: hit_count ∈ [3, 1_000_000], category in whitelist (logic|safety|performance|security|ux|governance), source_agent_id ≤ 128 byte, content ≤ 8KB, title ≤ 256 char.
- **feat(handlers)**: `handlers_brain_mistakes.go` (LOCKED) — `POST /api/mistakes/submit` body {agent_id, category, title, content, hit_count} return {id, added}. `GET /api/mistakes?tier=&source=&limit=` (default 50, max 500). MaxBytesReader 32KB. DisallowUnknownFields.
- **verified end-to-end via 7 scenario**:
  - Schema clean, 4 index + UNIQUE
  - Valid submit: id=1, added=true
  - Re-submit: id=1, added=false, hit_count 5→8
  - Invalid hit_count < 3: rejected
  - Invalid category 'xyz': rejected
  - List returns 1 row with tier='global'
  - hit_count = 99999999999: rejected (cap 1M)
  - agent_id 130 char: rejected (cap 128)
  - Atomic UPSERT verified: fresh insert id=2 added=true, immediate re-submit id=2 added=false (no race window)

### Phase 1 scope (DONE):
- Schema + validate + atomic UPSERT + admin endpoint.

### Audit critical fixes (3) applied BEFORE lock:
- **C1 (hit_count overflow)**: rejected only `< 3`, max int64 (~9.2e18) allowed → caller submit huge value, subsequent increment wraps negative in SQLite. Fixed: cap `maxHitCount = 1_000_000`.
- **C2 (exported whitelist map mutable shared state)**: `MistakeCategoryWhitelist` exported map can be mutated globally. Fixed: privatize to `mistakeCategoryWhitelist`, expose `IsValidMistakeCategory()` + `ListMistakeCategories()` accessor.
- **C3 (TOCTOU race SELECT-then-INSERT)**: 2 concurrent submitter both miss SELECT, both INSERT → UNIQUE constraint fail → opaque 400 to 2nd. Fixed: single atomic `INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE SET ... RETURNING id, hit_count`. isNew distinguished via `hit_count == submitted` (fresh insert = newCount equals submitted value).

### Important fix:
- **#4 source_agent_id length cap**: 128 byte limit anti index bloat.

### Defer phase 2:
- Brain_antibody auto-promotion (cross-reference dengan AddDrawerFull wing='antibody')
- WebSocket notify warga lain
- `/api/mistakes/promote` admin manual promote endpoint
- Rate limit (defer reverse-proxy layer)
- agent_id format validation (e.g. regex match kernel warga list)
- Content XSS escape (UI render concern, JSON safe)

